<paragraph blockId="21.[146,976,194,597]" pageId="21" pageNumber="144">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[170,333,548,570]" pageId="21" pageNumber="144">Specific epithet.</emphasis>
The name is the comparative of the Latin adjective 
<emphasis box="[910,975,549,570]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="144">parvus</emphasis>
meaning smaller.
</paragraph>
